<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= briefing.subject %> | CH-AIDE 브리핑</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="header-inner">
      <div>
        <h1>📋 CH-AIDE 브리핑</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">ch-aide@aidepartners.com 수신 PDF 자동 브리핑</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/" class="btn-check">← 목록으로</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="detail-card">
      <div class="detail-meta">
        <span class="badge">📅 <%= briefing.mail_date %></span>
        <span class="badge">📄 <%= briefing.pdf_filename %></span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="detail-title"><%= briefing.subject %></h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div class="detail-content">
        <% const lines = briefing.pdf_content.split('\n'); %>
        <% lines.forEach(line => { %>
          <% if (line.trim()) { %>
            <p><%= line %></p>
          <% } %>
        <% }) %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>1시간마다 자동으로 메일을 확인합니다.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
